    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for those who prioritize utility over aesthetics. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a few small dents, and the interior shows significant wear on the upholstery and carpets. While the car runs and drives, it will likely require some mechanical attention in the near future, such as new tires and a brake service. All major systems like the air conditioning and radio are functional, though they show their age. This is an honest, budget-friendly option for someone looking for a functional car that doesn't need to be perfect.",
