    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new ride that still has tons of life left in it? I'm parting with this beauty, and it's honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape, super clean, and ready for all your upcoming road trips! I've taken great care of it, and I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm super easy to talk to and can't wait to show it to you!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Available for sale is a driver-focused E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six engine with its factory-spec 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This example retains its mechanical integrity with a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a functioning M-Variable Differential Lock. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement, ensuring the chassis remains rigid under high lateral loads. The suspension features upgraded bushings for improved turn-in response, and the braking system utilizes cross-drilled rotors for effective heat dissipation. While showing signs of respectful use, the powertrain remains robust, delivering linear torque and that signature metallic rasp. A mechanically sound enthusiast machine ready for the twisties.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Regular maintenance performed. Clean interior. Reliable performance. Title in hand.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This vehicle is the perfect marriage of performance and practicality. The exterior finish remains vibrant and glossy, with only the slightest signs of careful use consistent with its age. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort, featuring well-preserved leather upholstery, a responsive infotainment system, and a sunroof that floods the space with light. Mechanically, this car stands out; it has been serviced religiously at every interval, resulting in a whisper-quiet engine and a transmission that delivers power seamlessly. It recently passed a full safety inspection and comes with a brand-new set of performance tires. For the buyer who values a documented history and a car that drives as well as it looks, this is an exceptional find.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies both reliability and sophisticated engineering. This unit offers a refined driving experience, featuring a preserved interior and a robust mechanical history. It represents an exceptional opportunity for the discerning buyer seeking a dependable, high-performance automobile that offers a significant value proposition without compromising on prestige.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it's been such a fantastic ride. It\u2019s in really solid shape, super reliable, and honestly just a joy to drive! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with a new owner today. If you're looking for something dependable and well-loved, this is the one for you. Drop me a message if you're interested!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
