    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused BMW E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant. This high-revving engine utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to provide exceptional throttle response up to its 7,900 RPM redline. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission delivers crisp engagement, paired with a torque-sensing limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery out of corners. Significant mechanical upkeep includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The chassis retains its razor-sharp handling characteristics thanks to refreshed bushings and a well-sorted suspension geometry. While the vehicle displays minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the mechanical synchronization and drivetrain integrity remain excellent. A visceral, analogue performance icon ready for the open road.",
